Dominic Coleman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dominic_Coleman 0 Dominic Andrew Coleman (born 29 January 1970 in Solihull, Warwickshire) is a British actor. He trained at Leeds University's Bretton Hall where he studied a BA (hons) in Dramatic Arts. He lives in London with his wife and children.
